channel.title: B e a t - t h e - w a t c h - Alphabet Challenge [CLOSED]
channel.description:
Hello! @anon86704580 and I are hosting our own kind of beat the clock! Here it is!
ALPHABET - You pick ONE letter, you can only use sounds/drum kits that start with that letter.
RULES: - - NO custom samples - NO custom drum kits - For the sake of scoring, please dont name any of the instruments. - YOU WILL BE DISQUALIFIED IF YOU USE AN INSTRUMENT THAT DOES NOT HAVE YOUR LETTER. - Keep it 30 seconds to 1 min 30, exceeding this by 5 seconds will result in a deduction in points.
SCORING - You will be scored in **3 ** areas out of 10 for each:
***QUALITY*** How good is the song?
***TIME*** Does the song comply with the time limit?
***CREATIVITY*** How does your song stand out?
Maximum of 40 points total
DEADLINE - You will have until **SATURDAY 26TH** to create and submit your song (GMT -4) (for all the Aussies not in Perth, the Sunday.)
SUBMITTING - Please submit your song ***IN THIS THREAD*** as an Auxy file link (export > render > export > share link) With your name, then your letter (e.g: Markiplier - E)
WINNERS - There will be a first, second and third winners announced when we finish scoring.
Let us know first that you're participating before submitting.
HAVE FUN -
-@FLB100
-@anon86704580
